# insert(_:)

**Instance Method**

Add a new model to the container. Returns true if added. Returns false if it already exists.

## Declaration

```swift
@discardableResult mutating func insert(_ model: MeshResource.Model) -> Bool
```

## Using the collection

- **count**: Number of models.
- **isEmpty**: True if there are no models.
- **remove(id:)**: Remove a model by id.
- **removeAll()**: Remove all the models.
- **update(_:)**: Update an existing model. The old model is returned.
